Interface ExcelSheet

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractExcelSheet, AbstractExcelSheetTest.MockExcelSheet, OCDSObjectExcelSheet

    public interface ExcelSheet
    Create an Excel Sheet representation of an Object of type T. In this process it's possible to create new Excel Sheet if some fields are annotated with ExcelExportSepareteSheet
